If your computer crashes while loading you problably
don't have enough free memory. Make sure that you have
at least 1.8 meg chip and about 1 meg fast.
If it still crashes, ther's probably a file missing
Try @{"installing" LINK "INSTALL"} it again.

If you have any trouble, please mail us and we'll
try to solve the problem.
We can't imagine there are any bugs in this game :)
but if you against all odds find any bugs,
